---
title: Chicken Teriyaki Bowls with Bell Pepper, Peanuts, and Sriracha
description: Forget takeout: the path to sweet-and-savory dinner bliss is as simple as breaking out a fry pan. In this recipe, chicken, pepper, and onion are coated in tantalizing teriyaki and peanuts are transformed into the perfect crunchy topping. Everything comes together over a bed of steamy white rice mixed with warm, sizzly ginger. The results? A symphony of flavors and textures that are so delicious, you might just lick the plate.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5d6041b97aa3c200155d10c6-3211c2da.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/chicken-teriyaki-stir-fry-5d6041b97aa3c200155d10c6-24017ae5.pdf
time required: 40 minutes
nutrition:
  calories: 790 kcal
