  saturated fat: 8 g
  carbohydrates: 93 g
  sugar: 23 g
  protein: 38 g
  fiber: 4 g
  sodium: 1360 mg
servings: 2
course: main course
author: Michelle Doll Olson
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/chicken-teriyaki-stir-fry-5d6041b97aa3c200155d10c6
cuisine: Asian
